dct_description_sm: Bundesamt gur Eich- und Vermessungswesen (Landesaufnahme) Relief shown by contour lines, shading and spot heights. Depth shown by contours and soundings in meters. "Zusammendruck aus der Osterreichschen Karte 1:50.000". Verso: Stadtplan von Salzburg (1:10,000). Map is filed under call number: G6494.S2C1.1949.S8. Accompanied by index (12 p.); Map Library does not have this index.
